{"tid":1759594,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"請即出示有效身份證明文件獲得名貴跑車一架","createTime":"2019-11-27T17:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T17:21:34.000Z","uid":90595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76b768d98c4f8cd731aa472bde6bcacea6e2b0d5","tid":1759594,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"咁就5年啦﹐仲記得第一次喺city識你嘅情景﹐仲記得自己著住hall5外套扮中學雞﹐而你冇帶con冇帶眼鏡連我都睇唔清。<br />\n「請即出示有效身份證明文件獲得名貴跑車一架」係我地搵番對方第一句我同你講嘅野。<br />\n然後好自然地日傾夜傾咁就一齊左。每次睇番紀錄你將「啦」打做「拉」我都忍唔住笑出聲。<br />\n然後dse出黎同你一齊溫書﹐補習做卷﹐特登轉場陪你考試﹐再然後你放榜因為成績差好徬徨一齊去搵asso﹐跟住我用左好多時間幫你排jupas。然後就係你番暑期工時晚晚接你收工同你一齊行番去...<br />\n然後中間好多好多回憶就唔再一一叙述﹐但好多好多畫面依然歷歷在目。<br />\n<br />\n原來轉眼間就已經5年﹐而家大個女啦﹐大學畢業啦。唔知你呢排過成點呢? 我地約好餐飯一直未找數﹐如果可以搵我食飯呀。"},{"pid":"bbabf86adc725e62439426fffbc7106989724b79","tid":1759594,"uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:51:17.000Z","msg":"冇人理您<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8230308af02ad59814f2bb0a74ee7acd1b084e5d","tid":1759594,"uid":90595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbabf86adc725e62439426fffbc7106989724b79","tid":1759594,"uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T18:51:17.000Z","msg":"冇人理您<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"在人群裏也可以是很寂寞的。<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/girls.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/671f86307567c8c3592d649265d5b018.jpg?auto=format&amp;q=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fgirls.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2F671f86307567c8c3592d649265d5b018.jpg%3F